57
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:32,000
So that's when something is frustrating.

58
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,000
I hate being frustrated.

59
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,000
Exactly.

60
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:44,000
