Is that right?

134
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:55,000
So he's ending the sentence with this phrase.

135
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,000
So he's making the sentence a question.

136
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,000
I see that you did this.

137
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,000
Is that right?

138
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:08,000
So he's asking her to confirm the fact that he knows about her because maybe they've never really talked before.

139
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:12,000
So this is a good way for him to ask her to give more details.

140
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,000
Exactly.

